short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Download images and videos exclusively from AliExpress.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The "AliExpress Video & Image Downloader Wizard" is a powerful Chrome extension designed to enhance your online shopping and browsing experience on AliExpress by providing a seamless and efficient way to download high-quality images and videos directly from product listings. With just a click, this extension allows users to effortlessly save their favorite product images and videos, making it easier to review, share, or keep a visual catalog of items of interest.
